data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom bungalow (ranch) home nestled on a spacious lot, offering both comfort and convenience. Step onto the full front porch which provides an inviting entryway to the home and can easily be styled with several rocking chairs or a nice porch swing.  Inside, you'll find a spacious interior with all appliances included, making move-in a breeze.  Conveniently located close to the city center, this home offers the perfect blend of suburban yard space and urban amenities such as parks and libraries. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a piece of history.  Sold as-is, this home is ready for you to make it your own! Perfect for investors looking to expand your portfolio. Schedule your showing today and experience the timeless appeal of this lovely property.
